<br>
Is this still the case?<br>
<br>
Why do I continue hearing people say that offhand is not linked to main hand and that it swings and checks on its own.<br>
 <p><center>
<a href="http://home.rochester.rr.com/grimmier/inner/main.htm"> <img src="http://www.inebraska.com/~mgarren/felwantag.jpg">
